                               Compile and Run                                    
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

• Build and run Audience

  If you don't have the source yet:
  bzr branch lp:audience
  cd audience
  mkdir build; cd build
  cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr
  make
  ./audience

• Bugs

  If you find bugs in this installation guide or in Audience itself, please report them at
  https://launchpad.net/audience/+filebug


